WebHDFS-Ruby is a ruby library for accessing WebHDFS REST APIs

In webhdfs.rb I used rest-client(require 'rest_client') for uploading files, 
because for now (Ruby 1.9.3), the ruby library net/http does not support multipart/form-data itself

To install rest-client, run command:
gem install rest-client

Development Environment:
Ubuntu 11.10
Ruby 1.9.3
Hadoop 1.0.1

References:
WebHDFS REST API http://hadoop.apache.org/common/docs/r1.0.0/webhdfs.html
webhdfs-py https://github.com/drelu/webhdfs-py/blob/master/webhdfs/webhdfs.py
